	signatures

6.0.1-10 (2024-02-26)

	Remove custom file.sh

6.0.1-9 (2023-12-17)

	Change default target triplet. Switch from 'pc' to 'unknown'.

6.0.1-8 (2023-03-06)

	Bug fix for file.sh. Don't attempt to extract all files.

6.0.1-7 (2023-03-05)

	Fix file.sh logic
	Try using tar early, before even calling 'file'
	Fix shellcheck warnings
	Swap tabs for spaces

6.0.1-6 (2023-03-05)

	Modify file.sh to better match detected file types

6.0.1-5 (2023-03-02)

	Improve the dotfiles check. Use find instead of shell globbing
	which seems to have changed behavior in bash-5.2, resulting in
	lots of false positives.

6.0.1-4 (2022-09-23)

	Add support for package signatures using asignify

6.0.1-3 (2021-09-12)

	Fix some subtle bugs in dependencies.sh, used in makepkg
	Adjust output of dependency check for easy listing of deps

6.0.1-2 (2021-09-10)

	Remove gpg/key-signing support again for now. Too many external
	dependencies. Will look at other options.

